de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.im.evaluate

Interface ImEvaluator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ImEvaluationComponent<ImObjectComponent>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ImcEvaluator, ImvEvaluator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractImEvaluatorIetf, DefaultImcEvaluator, DefaultImvEvaluator

    interface ImEvaluator
extends ImEvaluationComponent<ImObjectComponent>
    Generic evaluator base. The evaluator holds several evaluation units and is responsible to measure exactly one instance of a component type (e.g. if there are two VPN clients to measure, there must be two evaluators.
